entries.femaleVariant: Nah, could never put on a tie, do an office gig. It's like I'm allergic to that sorta work.
Come on. Not like they wouldn't train you.
I mean it, wouldn't last a month in a place like that. Wouldn't have a life.
You got no ambition. Me, I ain't tryin' to stay here my whole life.
What, think you'll have a career in a corp? Choom, no offense, but you're a nobody.
They can dress you up, but you'll still be a nobody. A nobody in a suit. 'Stead of standin' here, you'll be brewin' coffee there.
